snippet.textDisplay: FUCK YA....O'Malley is back FINALLY.  Fuckin' USADA, man I hope he got even more savage.  That record needs to stay undefeated...time for the Sugar Show!!! Being suspended 2 times for tiny amounts of Osterine from a tainted supplement is almost unheard of.  USADA even said the amount in his system wasn't performance enhancing.  He got so popular so fast, and honestly...he was a little small and not a complete fighter.  I think Dana wanted him to recover from his leg injury, train hard, get bigger, and be the next big cash cow.  He's got that star quality for sure...he's so fun to watch.  He's on the undercard and they put him on Embedded...that shows you the popularity right there.  They NEVER do that, already hypin' him up.
